cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.CL

This paper is about reducing communication bandwidth in distributed deep learning training systems, which is a topic closely related to machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The experiments in the paper involve image classification (cs.CV) and language modeling (cs.CL) tasks, which further support these categories. Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques to improve performance, which could also fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
